{"tid":1015164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃世澤：《時聞香港》劉轉好做國安人員被點相","createTime":"2019-02-09T17:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T17:29:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8aefab37b41a0a08ab135b64ec580ce053c10a5d","tid":1015164,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/24652/時聞香港-劉轉好做國安人員被點相\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F24652%2F%E6%99%82%E8%81%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%8A%89%E8%BD%89%E5%A5%BD%E5%81%9A%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E9%BB%9E%E7%9B%B8&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=dcd77705\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/24652/時聞香港-劉轉好做國安人員被點相</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://x7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/時聞香港-劉轉好-國安-min-768x449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F%E6%99%82%E8%81%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%8A%89%E8%BD%89%E5%A5%BD-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89-min-768x449.jpg&h=97b4bcae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃世澤<br />\n<br />\n我幾時都話，幫啲五毛同大公文匯記者點相好重要，依家所言非虛，香港大學一個活動上面，當時事評論員盧斯達發音嘅時候， 時聞香港 劉轉好係咁影周圍參與啲人嘅相，結果佢被人圍住。講真，香港叫斯文，喺以前嘅台灣或者南洋，條友被人開咗年，血光之災都有份。<br />\n<br />\n時聞香港 劉轉好係典型國安行為<br />\n<br />\n時聞香港 劉轉好，以至愛黨力呢啲人，甚至啲五毛係要逐個點相，呢個係中國維權運動嘅經驗歸納出嚟。"},{"pid":"d430d304e3c1a10b5417dd68a5fc4a5b778006d6","tid":1015164,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"呢條乞兒五毛黎"},{"pid":"d519598da9d77feaec9b1c96b52479c4b5bd3bfb","tid":1015164,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"黃世澤：劉轉好係國安<br />\n<br />\n總結：劉轉好只係提供外判服務嘅自僱人士"}]}